Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rise once more! Rise once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru! Yomigaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rise once more! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.07,0:01:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Escape
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Concentrate fire to starboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow.\NHow are the Guncannon and Guntank?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're still active.\NApproaching entrance to enemy base!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Attacking from outside isn't\Ngetting us anywhere...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let Mr. Kai have all the fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.91,0:02:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! I was the first one who landed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I warned you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:02:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't attack from all directions\Nwhen I'm this close! Hey, Char?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.27,0:03:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you get Lalah involved?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.07,0:03:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah was never meant to be a warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Snap out of it!\NDon't you die on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the rest to the mobile suits!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That Gundam pilot..."Amuro", was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do?\NHow can I beat that Newtype...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah. Please tell me.\NWhat should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut down the engines immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- Cut off the engines. Mirai!\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're touching down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to you. Tell all hands\Nto prepare for hand-to-hand combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The controls, they're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.19,0:04:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your surroundings!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know where\Nthe enemy will come from!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Both the White Base engines are blown!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Is everyone okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- Tell Kai and Hayato to cover us!\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- Fraw Bow, get a sidearm.\N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Char?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Damn Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.77,0:05:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over!\NI've only lost the main camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Zeong's been shot down!\NIdentification signal canceled!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The Red Comet has fallen from the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- N Field, no response!\N- S Field, no response! What?! Missiles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Send ammo to Block 24 of W Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Snakel, Snakel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Gundam pilot has developed\Nexceptionally because he's a Newtype...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...then perhaps this was inevitable.\NDon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.07,0:05:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Your Excellency!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender this base\N15 minutes after my escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But, ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go while Granada and\Nthe homeland have fighting strength left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But escaping at this point would be\Nalmost impossible, ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I survive, Zeon is not lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What will happen to me after we surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.22,0:06:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll get you back in a prisoner exchange.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- Get my ship ready.\N- Right away, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is crawling with the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy ground troops are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands, counter with bazookas and rifles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Char must realize the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Zabi family\Nthat needs to be brought down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's he getting in the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Char...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe I now have the ability\Nto defeat the true enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can sense the Zabi family leader is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have received\Nthose powers from Lalah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one that drew Lalah into the war!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't forgive that,\Nyou're misguided, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If not for the war, Lalah never\Nwould have awakened as a Newtype.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just an excuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's the correct point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.58,0:08:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Come any closer and I'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Newtypes like yourself are\Ntoo dangerous right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!\NYou call that "covering the White Base"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand-to-hand combat, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's all over the place out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Send us a Dom company!\NJust one Zanzibar isn't enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious!\NWe have no intention of dying here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Send us escorts, even if they're just Zakus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is there a delay?\N- I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Make them hurry!\NDon't let the other soldiers figure things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.61,0:09:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The company commander's\Nin trouble in Block 24!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- They've begun ground combat?\N- Up ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you're the strongest soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the true enemy the Zabi family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in my case!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea why I lured you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you figured that a Newtype\Nhas to use their body like an ordinary person!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Even a Newtype must\Nbe trained for physical skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.53,0:10:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your theory!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.21,0:10:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Amuro! Stop it, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You two don't have to fight each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because there's a war going on\Ndoesn't mean you two have to...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah just told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...that Newtypes aren't meant to be\Ntools for destroying each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In the battlefield, they're powerful weapons.\NThat's just the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're a Newtype yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this! Both of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- Artesia...\N- Please, brother! Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't any reason to hate Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't accept him as my enemy,\NI have to get him when I have the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought your enemy was the Zabi family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroying that family is no longer\Nmy top priority, Artesia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Once Zeon is no more,\Nwe will enter the age of Newtypes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If young Amuro can understand\Nwhat I'm trying to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then become my comrade-in-arms.\NIt would make Lalah happy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:11:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother! How could you even suggest that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother! Is your forehead wounded...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for this helmet, I'd be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew Lady Kycilia would be escaping.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:13:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I had wanted to escort her myself.\NBut unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, perhaps you could...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll protect\NHer Excellency on your behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The rumors of burns on your face\Nwere not true, it seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The air here's getting pretty thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out now, Artesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But what will you do, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.47,0:13:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've realized that I can't just\Nlet a Zabi go free, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to settle the score.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Casval...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an adult already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.44,0:13:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Become a good woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Amuro is calling for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where's Lady Kycilia?!\N- She's about to take off, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Salamis approaching from above!\NWe'll take off at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Down on the floor if you don't have a seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,10! 9!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Garma, here's a farewell present.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you'll get along with your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Char?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I can't return to the others anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.55,0:15:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And... if I did... if... I did make it...\NMy brother couldn't have...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this... the end for me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I might make it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the White Base crew?\NAnd Ms. Sayla?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I going to join Lalah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Newtypes shouldn't be killing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:15:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...You're right. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can play with you anytime, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.54,0:16:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see them! Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! You can see things, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Ms. Sayla! Stand up!\NGet up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro?! Is that you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...But... I don't know where I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I should go straight ahead...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And after you've gone 500 meters,\Nmake a 90 degree left turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,After 500 meters...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Seal off hatch 16!\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.03,0:17:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll all die if we don't abandon ship...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Seal off the hatch!\NWe don't have any allies left over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.04,0:17:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have them prepare the launches!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Fraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time the firing stops,\Nyou can run through safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's you. Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.84,0:17:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to the launches! Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When I start running, you run too. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.41,0:17:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Argh! They're all aiming at the White Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.06,0:18:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This ship stands out too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- Did you hear that?\N- Yeah. It's Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- He says we should retreat now!\N- I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.09,0:18:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Federation Forces seem to be winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're winning,\Nwe should be okay to retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- We've got you!\N- Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. It looks good. Let's take them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base is... going down...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If Amuro hadn't called out to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...those flames would have enveloped us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you telling me\NAmuro isn't on this launch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he's not. Sayla, you and Mirai\Nwould be able to hear Amuro better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?\N- Sayla. You're the daughter of Zeon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're closer to a Newtype.\NPlease, search for Amuro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But... But... How do I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro's the only one missing. Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.73,0:19:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How can I possibly know that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.69,0:19:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard Amuro's voice just now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I could hear him so clearly\Nuntil I got to the White Base...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.89,0:20:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Human beings can't\Nchange themselves so conveniently...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! A little to the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.34,0:20:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah! Right!\N- Okay! Now straight forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?! You three...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah! This way! This way! Just do it!\N- This way! It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're almost outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.77,0:20:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell?!\NWh-Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,4! 3! 2! 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I still do have a place to go home to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And nothing could make me happier!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:21:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll understand, won't you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:21:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can go to see you anytime, Lalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Universal Century 0080.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.19,0:22:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,After this battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:22:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...a peace treaty was concluded...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.26,0:23:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...between the Earth Federation Government\Nand the Republic of Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.15,0:23:24.99,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.99,0:23:29.99,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:40.21,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.21,0:23:45.13,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.13,0:23:49.76,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.76,0:23:55.15,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.15,0:23:59.73,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.73,0:24:10.04,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.15,0:23:24.99,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.99,0:23:29.99,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:40.21,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.21,0:23:45.13,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.13,0:23:49.76,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.76,0:23:55.15,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.15,0:23:59.73,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.73,0:24:10.04,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
